<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Information Sheet</h1>
    <p><strong>HONG KONG METROPOLITAN UNIVERSITY</strong></p>
    <p><strong>Acceptability of a Combined Respiratory Influenza-Covid-19 Vaccine Among Nursing Students in Hong Kong </strong></p>
    <p><strong>Information for Participants</strong></p>
    <p><strong>November 2025</strong></p>
    <p>Thank you for participating in this research study. As a nursing student, your insights are valuable for understanding attitudes toward emerging vaccines that could protect both healthcare workers and patients from multiple respiratory viruses. This survey is anonymous, takes about 10-15 minutes, and your responses will help inform public health strategies. Participation is voluntary, and you may withdraw at any time. No personally identifying information will be collected. By proceeding, you consent to participate. If you have questions, contact the Principal Investigator Prof. Eddy Lam at 3970 2992.</p>
    <p>This study has been approved by the Research Ethics Committee (REC) of The Hong Kong Metropolitan University. REC Reference No.: <strong>HE-SF2025/64</strong>.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="/survey" class="btn">Agree to Participate</a>
      <a href="/goodbye" class="btn btn-secondary" id="disagree-btn">Disagree</a>
    </p>
    <p><a href="/downloads" class="info-link">Download Survey Data (Admin Access)</a></p>
    <p>Yours sincerely,<br>Professor Eddy Lam<br>Principal Investigator<br>School of Nursing and Health Sciences<br>Hong Kong Metropolitan University</p>
  </div>
  
  <script>
    // Listen for click on the Disagree button
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
